data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value: SELECT dbo.tRSPNOSI.transCode, dbo.tRSPNOSI.EIC, dbo.tRSPNOSI.itemNo, dbo.tRSPNOSI.fullNameFirst, dbo.vRSPEmployee.fullNameTitle, dbo.tRSPNOSI.lastNamePrefix, dbo.vRSPEmployee.namePrefix, dbo.vRSPEmployee.lastName, dbo.tRSPNOSI.effectiveDate, dbo.tRSPNOSI.positionTitle, dbo.tRSPNOSI.salaryGrade, dbo.tRSPNOSI.stepIncFrom, dbo.tRSPNOSI.salaryFrom, dbo.tRSPNOSI.salaryDetailCode, dbo.tRSPNOSI.stepIncTo, dbo.tRSPNOSI.salaryTo, dbo.tRSPNOSI.salaryAdd, dbo.tRSPNOSI.printedDate, dbo.tRSPNOSI.fy, dbo.tRSPNOSI.nosiTag, dbo.tRSPNOSI.remarks, dbo.vRSPEmployee.departmentName, dbo.tOrgDepartment.branch FROM dbo.tRSPNOSI LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.vRSPEmployee ON dbo.tRSPNOSI.EIC = dbo.vRSPEmployee.EIC LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.tOrgDepartment ON dbo.vRSPEmployee.departmentCode = dbo.tOrgDepartment.departmentCode WHERE transCode = @paramCode
